languages.text: “我是基亚瓦伽马星的{mf|主人|女主人}。既然这些人是我的臣民，那只有我有权决定如何处置他们。我命令所有围观人员立刻离开。至于剩下的人，去码头那边，等待我进一步指示。”
languages.original_text: "I am the {mf|master|mistress} of Kiava Gamma, and if these people are my subjects, then I am the only one who can decide what to do with them. I command the onlookers to disperse, as for the rest of you — go to the docks and await further instructions."

languages.text: «Soy {mf|el señor|la señora} de Kiava Gamma. Estas personas son mis súbditos, por lo que soy responsable de decidir qué hacer con ellos. Ordeno que los curiosos se dispersen y que el resto vaya al puerto a aguardar nuevas instrucciones».
languages.original_text: "I am the {mf|master|mistress} of Kiava Gamma, and if these people are my subjects, then I am the only one who can decide what to do with them. I command the onlookers to disperse, as for the rest of you — go to the docks and await further instructions."

languages.text: « Je suis {mf|le maître|la maîtresse} de Kiava Gamma. Si ces gens sont réellement mes sujets, je suis la seule personne en position de décider de leur sort. Que tous les badauds rentrent chez eux. Vous autres, rendez-vous sur les quais, puis attendez de nouvelles instructions. »
languages.original_text: "I am the {mf|master|mistress} of Kiava Gamma, and if these people are my subjects, then I am the only one who can decide what to do with them. I command the onlookers to disperse, as for the rest of you — go to the docks and await further instructions."

Que tous les badauds rentrent chez eux. Vous autres, rendez-vous sur les quais, puis attendez de nouvelles instructions. »

languages.text: "Ich bin {mf|der Herr|die Herrin} von Kiava Gamma, und wenn diese Leute meine Untertanen sind, kann auch nur ich entscheiden, was mit ihnen geschehen soll. Ich befehle, dass die Umstehenden sich entfernen, und was den Rest von Euch angeht – geht zu den Docks und wartet auf weitere Anweisungen."

languages.text: "Kiava Gama'nın efendisi benim. Bu insanlar da benim tebaam. Hâliyle akıbetlerine de ben karar veririm. Kalabalığın dağılmasını emrediyorum. Sizler de rıhtıma gidip talimatlarımı bekleyin."
languages.original_text: "I am the {mf|master|mistress} of Kiava Gamma, and if these people are my subjects, then I am the only one who can decide what to do with them. I command the onlookers to disperse, as for the rest of you — go to the docks and await further instructions."

traits.locale_text: "Ben Kiava Gama'nın efendisiyim ve bu insanlar benim tebaalarımsa, onlara ne olacağına karar verecek olan da benimdir. Kalabalığın dağılmasını emrediyorum. Siz ise rıhtıma gidin ve vereceğim talimatları bekleyin."
